data.description: Opportunity is here! This end townhome on the 18th green is three levels of living space waiting for the finishing touches! Being an end unit has its advantages. This unit has a front balcony, back deck and patio space under the deck for plenty of areas to get fresh air and enjoy the view of the course. The updates on this home so far include: new electrical, new plumbing, new flooring, new tub/showers, new dishwasher & disposal, new kitchen cabinets and counters, and more. Additional materials on site for incomplete projects. Now is the perfect time to step in and make the finishing touches match your preferred style! See Agent Remarks
